onics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1306" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ad93dca0-2711-11ee-bffb-5c2ddddbf361" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1306" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ad93dca0-2711-11ee-bffb-5c2ddddbf361" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Devindra Hardawar/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Apple MacBook Air M1]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple MacBook Air M1]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Summer Samsung Unpacked 2023: What to expect on July 26th]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>三星今年稍早<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-will-unveil-its-new-foldables-on-july-26th-230053235.html">于 7 月 26 日</a>举办夏季 Unpacked 活动，但它承诺的特别之处不仅仅在于时间安排。 Galaxy Z 可折叠手机<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL25ld3Muc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vZ2xvYmFsL2VkaXRvcmlhbC11bnBhY2tpbmctdGhlLWRlc2lnbnMtYW5kLWlubm92YXRpb25zLWluc3BpcmVkLWJ5LXlvdSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNmMyYzBlODgtMmQ1MS00ZGM0LThkMTYtMjc4ZTRhOTRiNDFkIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAT_w_j3k5LMSyZP8Cv2pG9K0ki